			<div class="clearfix">

				<span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://www.thenewcivilrightsmovement.com/author/dbadash/">David Badash</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><a href="https://www.thenewcivilrightsmovement.com/2019/02/as-10-states-cope-with-measles-crisis-top-trump-officials-anti-vaxx-wife-issues-call-to-bring-back-deadly-diseases/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2019-02-13T14:26:32+00:00">February 13, 2019<span class="entry-time">2:26 PM</span></time><time class="updated" hidden datetime="2019-02-13T14:32:50+00:00">February 13, 2019</time></a></span>
